.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Documentation
*.md
!README.md
docs/
ARCHITECTURE_DIAGRAM.md
BRUTE_FORCE_PROTECTION.md
IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md
PRODUCTION_DEPLOYMENT_SUMMARY.md
QUICK_REFERENCE.md
QUICK_START.md
REDIS_DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md
REDIS_SETUP_GUIDE.md

